Detailed Description

Represents a parameter, that is, a GeoXmlParameterGroup or a GeoXmlParameter.

Define Documentation

#define GEOXML_PARAMETER ( super   )     ((GeoXmlParameter*)(super))

Get the base parameter class of super , which can be a GeoXmlParameterGroup or GeoXmlParameter instance.

Typedef Documentation

typedef struct geoxml_parameter GeoXmlParameter

The GeoXmlParameter struct contains private data only, and should be accessed using the functions below.

Enumeration Type Documentation

enum GEOXML_PARAMETERTYPE

GEOXML_PARAMETERTYPE lists the program's parameters types supported by libgeoxml.

They were made to create a properly link between the seismic processing softwares and this library.

See also:
geoxml_parameter_get_is_program_parameter
Enumerator:
GEOXML_PARAMETERTYPE_UNKNOWN  In case of error.
GEOXML_PARAMETERTYPE_STRING  A parameter able to store a string on it.
GEOXML_PARAMETERTYPE_INT  A parameter able to store an integer number on it.
GEOXML_PARAMETERTYPE_FILE  A parameter able to store a file/directory path on it.
GEOXML_PARAMETERTYPE_FLAG  A parameter able to store the state of a flag on it.
GEOXML_PARAMETERTYPE_FLOAT  A parameter able to store a floating point number on it.
GEOXML_PARAMETERTYPE_RANGE  A parameter able to store a number with maximum and minimum values on it.
GEOXML_PARAMETERTYPE_ENUM  A parameter able to store a value in a list options.
GEOXML_PARAMETERTYPE_GROUP  A sequence of parameters.
GEOXML_PARAMETERTYPE_REFERENCE  A reference to other parameter.

If the referenced parameter is a program parameter, then this parameter will only have its value as a difference.

gboolean geoxml_parameter_set_type ( GeoXmlParameter *  parameter,
enum GEOXML_PARAMETERTYPE  type 
)

Change parameter type to type.

Only label of parameter will have the same value after the change; all other properties will have their value lost.

If parameter is NULL nothing is done.

GeoXmlParameter *  reference 
)

Change parameter to reference reference.

Return one of GEOXML_RETV_SUCCESS, GEOXML_RETV_REFERENCE_TO_ITSELF, GEOXML_RETV_NULL_PTR

enum GEOXML_PARAMETERTYPE geoxml_parameter_get_type ( GeoXmlParameter *  parameter  ) 

Returns parameter 's type.

GEOXML_PARAMETERTYPE_REFERENCE is not returned here. The "true" type of the parameter is returned instead.

If parameter is NULL returns GEOXML_PARAMETERTYPE_UNKNOWN.

GeoXmlParameter* geoxml_parameter_get_referencee ( GeoXmlParameter *  parameter_reference  ) 

If parameter_reference is of the type GEOXML_PARAMETERTYPE_REFERENCE returns the parameter that it references.

Otherwise, returns NULL.

If parameter_reference is NULL returns NULL.

gboolean geoxml_parameter_get_is_program_parameter ( GeoXmlParameter *  parameter  ) 

Return TRUE if parameter is a GeoXmlProgramParameter.

All parameters of any GEOXML_PARAMETERTYPE's types except GEOXML_PARAMETERTYPE_GROUP are GeoXmlProgramParameter.

If parameter is NULL returns FALSE.
